body: Hi, I have the latest version of Ladybug and Honeybee installed in my computer and working fine until this morning !! When I turned my computer this morning, the LB and HB components are missing from the tabs bar as shown in the screenshot [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/ExlLp5DNAJ8DDwSIZTK32ENmkx*VxySg5ycaLFbCxdppTfThNbQhrYg8anreJmqtoOQQ30-Wt1Thv4T-TxW-WlIrlqhmxg4V/Untitled.png) When I checked the User Object folder, I can see all the files there. I removed LB&HB and reinstalled it and still the same issue. When I open an old script, I can see all the components in GH canvas and I can run the script. Has anyone faced this issue before? Or do you know how can I fix it? Thank you, Mohammed
